1025
01:51:37,433 --> 01:51:41,733
- He's in custody. They're bringing him down.
- SWAT team's at 42nd Street.

1026
01:51:43,172 --> 01:51:45,402
- Are you all right?.
- Yeah. Where's Zuwanie?.

1027
01:51:45,608 --> 01:51:48,270
- The safe room. What happened?.
- It was a fake.

1028
01:51:48,478 --> 01:51:52,710
A piece of theatre to justify the killing.
Ethnic cleansing, genocide.

1029
01:51:52,915 --> 01:51:56,146
You there?. That's the flight. She's not on it.

1030
01:51:56,352 --> 01:51:58,912
I checked every hotel in New York,
her friends.

1031
01:51:59,122 --> 01:52:02,148
They don't know where she'd go.
No one knows her.

1032
01:52:02,358 --> 01:52:05,486
- I know her.
- OK, where is she?.

1033
01:52:05,695 --> 01:52:08,892
