- How'd you happen to be there after hours?.
- (Silvia) An evacuation. I left some things.

1036
01:52:14,871 --> 01:52:17,738
It takes too long...
I wouldn 't mind if he were gone.

1037
01:52:17,940 --> 01:52:20,408
